This Product Addendum supplements and modifies the terms of the Rovel Stars
Software License (RSSL) v1.0 with additional, product-specific terms for the
above product. It applies only to the named product and to any Forks or
Derivative Works of that product as defined in the RSSL.  

In the event of any conflict between this Addendum and the RSSL, this Addendum
shall govern with respect to the product-specific matters described herein.

