2. ADDITIONAL DEFINITIONS
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Define any terms that apply specifically to this product.

Example:
2.1 “Edition” means any named variant or configuration of the product (e.g.,
     Community Edition, Enterprise Edition, Server Edition).
2.2 “Official Update Channel” means the Rovel Stars-maintained service through
     which signed updates, patches, or upgrades for this product are
     distributed.
2.3 “Partner” means an authorized organization certified by Rovel Stars to
     distribute, preinstall, or support this product under an approved program.

